33
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:52,550
and stay with you,

34
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:55,070
and I fell asleep.

35
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,510
Don't worry,

36
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:01,590
I won't take advantage of you
when you're drunk.

37
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:10,040
Yue,

38
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,990
I've fallen in love with you
since college.

39
00:05:16,810 --> 00:05:18,430
You only know I died once,

40
00:05:18,930 --> 00:05:20,990
