what I've been through.

41
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:23,100
I know everything.

42
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,290
Sorry, Yue,

43
00:05:24,300 --> 00:05:25,230
I investigated you.

44
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,390
I just wanted to know who you are.

45
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:29,830
I found the plastic surgery hospital

46
00:05:31,790 --> 00:05:33,870
and the apartment you once lived in.

47
00:05:34,490 --> 00:05:36,000
I know what you've been through.

48
00:05:36,410 --> 00:05:37,990
However, if you don't move on,

49
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,910
you can never forget the past.

50
00:05:40,170 --> 00:05:42,400
God has given you a chance to live

51
00:05:42,410 --> 00:05:44,230
and given me a chance to love you.

52
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,150
I don't want to lose you again.

53
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,550
Can you be my girlfriend?

54
